description:
On the night of his brother`s wedding, Dale comes to terms with his position among the Teathrow, and the course of events that led him to meet Latina.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Le jeune homme et la fillette au mariage
Seinen, otouto no kekkonshiki to osanai shoujo to.
The Young Man Attends His Brother`s Wedding with the Young Girl.
青年, 弟の結婚式と幼い少女と.
